text: Bianca Desai or Biyanka Desai is an Indian film actress who works in Kannada, Tamil and Telugu films. ==Career== Bianca Desai has been part of more than 9 films in Kannada. ==Selected filmography== * Gulama (2009) * This Weekend (2012) * Rocky (2008) * Chellidaru Sampigeya (2009) * Kiccha Huccha (2010) * Sanchari(2010) * Swayam Krushi (2011) *Noorondu bagilu (2019) ==See also== *List of people from Karnataka *Cinema of Karnataka *List of Indian film actresses *Cinema of India ==References== Category:Actresses in Kannada cinema Category:Actresses in Tamil cinema Category:Living people Category:Kannada people Category:Actresses from Karnataka Category:Indian film actresses Category:21st-century Indian actresses Category:Actresses in Kannada television Category:Year of birth missing (living people)
